Below a JSDOC comment which does not show properly in document type javascript.

```
// Interface new functions
/**
 * @param  {Object} to
 * @param  {Object} from
 * @param  {Boolean|String} override=false
 */
function Interface(to,from,override) {
       // some code
    }
```

It always shows **"to:any, from:any, override:any"**
why not **"to:any, from:any, override:Boolean=false|String"** or something simular
